after we log even WHEN put in the bank! I declare<BR>
Shananogens(spck) on this vile &quot;enhancement!&quot;  This <BR>
just isn't right! Now our chances of selling our <BR>
weapons, bandages, and other items of the sort will<BR>
probably decrease! I'm not going ramble on about this<BR>
but, I think it's just not fair. It puts us at a<BR>
disadvantage. Heh, if they're going to do that why<BR>
not take away kiting? For one it's cheap, and it puts <BR>
SoW casters at a serious unfair advantage over the <BR>
other classes.  Or, even better yet, let EVERYONE cast<BR>
SoW! Anyhow, I may have jumped off subject there, but<BR>
if anything, at least allow some of our conjured items <BR>
to remain permanent, not all, but some to compensate this<BR>
&quot;enhancement.&quot; I'll most likely petition agianst this, and <BR>
